{"tid":1106408,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"途人聞槍聲衝入商舖避險","createTime":"2019-04-14T14:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T18:33:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b78eea71738e3608a864e84233b269aca2868ced","tid":1106408,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190414/20655743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F20655743&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjvSLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=f8520cba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190414%2F20655743&h=9186aa67\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190414/20655743</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n途人聞槍聲衝入商舖避險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190414/large/a0204a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190414%2Flarge%2Fa0204a.gif&h=bc93bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名途人在槍擊案發生後爭相衝入附近零食舖躲避。閉路電視片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】長沙灣道前晚發生槍擊案時，街上有不少行人，驟聞「砰」的一聲巨響，眾人擔心被流彈所傷爭相走避，部份人躲入店舖要求店員關閘，其中一間零食店更一度有十多人衝入，場面混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：湖南幫四代插旗 雄霸九成市場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190414/large/a0204b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190414%2Flarge%2Fa0204b.gif&h=321cbbdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n神情驚慌狂叫關閘<br />\n<br />\n該間零食店距離開槍現場逾30米，負責該案的西九龍總區重案組探員昨返現場搜證，翻看該店於案發前後的閉路電視錄影片段。片段顯示，前晚約10時15分，店外人流熙來攘往，突然十多名男女神色慌張地衝入店內，相信是在聽到槍聲後受驚躲入零食店，其後部份人朝店外走，站在店門口東張西望，相信是想了解槍聲過後街上情況。<br />\n<br />\n現場附近一間手機配件店姓謝店員指，事發時聽到疑似爆胎聲音，但因店舖正在播歌故聽不清楚，未幾多名在店外巴士站候車的市民衝入店內，他們表現驚慌，不停叫「關閘」，其中一名女子更跌倒在地。謝擔心外面再有人開槍，即時拉閘，約五分鐘後才重新開閘。<br />\n<br />\n對於發生鬧市開槍案，街坊議論紛紛坦言很擔心，伍女士說：「喺度住咗成30年，近年多咗好多南亞人，都驚驚哋，治安冇以前咁好。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者文兆麟  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n湖南幫四代插旗 雄霸九成市場<br />\n<br />\n湖南幫四代插旗 雄霸九成市場<br />\n干擾器出千穿煲釣魚機賭檔講數 黑漢槍傷湖南仔"},{"pid":"99c22c1635d6b5388f96307af3c198339bf60694","tid":1106408,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"3ef1441996d30788718fbd2eb48697d6a950e2c2","tid":1106408,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b73acec371fd565cd080f1ea9b12525ca92e3e1","tid":1106408,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T17:37:15.000Z","msg":"無啦啦衝入人地舖頭就叫人閂閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都要聽晒我話。"},{"pid":"d44d1d402ef04743c8dd5f352562260bcaa8f8a7","tid":1106408,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b73acec371fd565cd080f1ea9b12525ca92e3e1","tid":1106408,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T17:37:15.000Z","msg":"無啦啦衝入人地舖頭就叫人閂閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都要聽晒我話。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T17:43:13.000Z","msg":"返返去50年代"},{"pid":"a89366de2498dd46cac3f5fab1e403731fada3e2","tid":1106408,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b73acec371fd565cd080f1ea9b12525ca92e3e1","tid":1106408,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T17:37:15.000Z","msg":"無啦啦衝入人地舖頭就叫人閂閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人人都要聽晒我話。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T17:52:23.000Z","msg":"店長：走呀！我要收工呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6261639c46674e974d006d238952717d1ad3fe","tid":1106408,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a89366de2498dd46cac3f5fab1e403731fada3e2","tid":110640